text: Mustapha Najjari (born 1951) is a Moroccan former cyclist. He competed in the individual road race event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1951 births Category:Living people Category:Moroccan male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Morocco Category:Cyclists at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Casablanca
